{"tid":401951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［民主黨表態］胡志偉：看不到港獨有出路，貼民主牆純粹嘩眾取寵","createTime":"2017-09-16T04:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T05:32:26.000Z","uid":41351,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eda2be915c94bcfc5a905a71f7cdd866840f8854","tid":401951,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:49:10.000Z","msg":"多所大專院校近日雖然被貼上「港獨」宣傳品，但各大學已清楚表明不同意「港獨」。民主黨主席胡志偉表示，看不到亦不相信「港獨」在香港會有出路。<br />\n不過，他認為由於各大學已表明反對「港獨」，因此毋須作強硬遏止。他又指，張貼「港獨」宣傳品的人士，無非是希望尋求大眾的注意而已。<br />\n<a href=\"http://toronto.singtao.ca/2054192/2017-09-15/post-民主黨胡志偉看不到「港獨」有出路/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftoronto.singtao.ca%2F2054192%2F2017-09-15%2Fpost-%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E3%80%8C%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8%E3%80%8D%E6%9C%89%E5%87%BA%E8%B7%AF%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=2WDnxmZy%2BccQqbbXIAbz3v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=46901340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://toronto.singtao.ca/2054192/2017-09-15/post-民主黨胡志偉看不到「港獨」有出路/?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"fc3b816dd06322e9e1622ee98613570d3142fa62","tid":401951,"uid":47565,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:50:39.000Z","msg":"我都睇唔到民主黨有咩出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d22816cdceff2bd7be6223a8ba9fa5ac6d844d9a","tid":401951,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike"